******************************************  Routes for Users  *******************************************************

POST - http://localhost/user/register
       
body - {
     "userId": 1
     "name": "xyz"
}

GET - http://localhost/user/allordersuserwise

GET - http://localhost/user/:userId


******************************************  Routes for orders  ********************************************************

Post - http://localhost/order/create

body - {
    "orderId":1,
    "userId": 1,
    "subtotal": 470,
    "date": "09/04/2020"
}

GET - http://localhost/order/userwiseorders

GET - http://localhost/order/:orderId